content: The first portable bag Museum in Asia, just on the avenue, happened to come for a pilgrimage. It still had a rich collection, few tourists, and it was clean, elegant and comfortable. From leather bags to jewelry, the design in the golden design era is really the best time.
The small handbag is also full of design and artistic sense, and each handbag is very delicate.

Here is a display of handbags from the 1500s to the present, you can understand the history and changes of handbags. The admission fee is 5000 won. There's a lot of leather here to make handbags, but it's expensive.
It's still a good museum. There must be a Chinese tour guide.
If you have time, you can go and see it. It's quite big.
